tantial feel.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eStraight baggy fit for comfortable, versatile wear.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eUnisex article suitable for a wide range of body types and style preferences.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eBack pocket for convenient storage.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eElasticated waist for a custom fit and added style.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eSoft, breathable jersey backing ensures all-day comfort and airflow.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003c\/ul\u003e","brand":"DRIP STUDIOS","offers":[{"title":"S","offer_id":46885165269146,"sku":"Reign4(-Copy 1)","price":1998.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false},{"title":"M","offer_id":46885165301914,"sku":"Reign4(-Copy 1)","price":1998.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false},{"title":"L","offer_id":46885165334682,"sku":"Reign4(-Copy 1)","price":1998.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false},{"title":"XS","offer_id":46885165367450,"sku":"Reign4(-Copy 1)","price":1998.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false},{"title":"XL","offer_id":46885165400218,"sku":"Reign4(-Copy 1)","price":1998.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false},{"title":"XXL","offer_id":46885165432986,"sku":"Reign4(-Copy 1)","price":1998.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0717\/2584\/2586\/files\/7D2C65F7-712E-4F7A-9CA9-16AE39530509.png?v=1769959695","url":"https:\/\/dripdrip.in\/products\/luxe-bottoms-melange-grey","provider":"DRIP STUDIOS","version":"1.0","type":"link"}